properties.Name: PolicyholderPaymentMethod
properties.Description: The Payment Method(s) that are acceptable (as standard or default Payment Methods) for sales transactions with the associated Policyholder.

Columns.Name: PolicyholderId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Policyholder.

Columns.Name: PaymentMethodId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Payment Method.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the Payment Method is defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the Payment Method is defined.

Columns.Name: PrimaryAlternatePaymentMethodIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the associated Payment Method is a primary or alternate Payment Method for the Policyholder.

Columns.Name: Note
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the standard or default Payment Method associated with the Policyholder.
